{"tid":967017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美角力】美署理防長履新 叫各軍種部長謹記「中國，中國，中國」","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T08:18:04.000Z","uid":8543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2980485825ed8e29e5b8ce0736d1f05045ba00f2","tid":967017,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"元旦履新的美國署理國防部長沙納漢（Patrick Shanahan），與各軍種的部長開會時，提醒他們謹記「中國，中國，中國」，可見他對中國的重視。<br />\n<br />\n國防部一名官員透露，沙納漢叫國防部要員着眼於國防戰略報告。該官員沒有闡釋沙納漢的中國觀，但有美國官員透露，沙納漢是國防部對華擺出強硬姿態的幕後推手，而去年美國國防戰略報告將就中俄視為戰略競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n馬蒂斯（Jim Mattis）上月宣佈辭任防長，總統特朗普委任國防部副部長沙納漢為署理防長。56歲的沙納漢沒有從軍經驗，沒有外交經驗，之前也無當官經驗，只當過波音飛機公司高層。不過，他執行力強，在國防部任職18個月，已交出多項政績，包括協助馬蒂斯把國防戰略重心由反恐轉向遏止中、俄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190103/59098839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59098839&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUXxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=298ec02b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59098839&h=92b49e37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190103/59098839</a>"},{"pid":"dbde8e5a0b66b636fa0d51301c2d3d2708f1ed1b","tid":967017,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RDrfE9I8_hs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRDrfE9I8_hs&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUXxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=94b4df93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RDrfE9I8_hs</a>"},{"pid":"d921afa35d762593b90615a1b70288ffc2460e32","tid":967017,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"Mr . Fix it<br />\n<br />\nBoeing uses him as its heavy hitter<br />\n<a href=\"http://articles.latimes.com/2008/feb/24/business/fi-sunprofile24\"